EAR NO EVIL*\n5L JC;, 9 Jo m J, Com,\nBy ELIZABETH ELLINGTON\n\"Thy Kingdom come.\"\nThy kingdom is come; Thou are ever-present.'\n\"Thy will be done in earth, as it is in heaven.\u201d\nEnable us to know, \u2014as in heaven, so on earth,\u2014God is\nomnipotent, supreme. (Science Health p. 16)\nTHE BIBLE TELLS US\n\"And it came to pass, when the time was come that he\nshould be received up, he stedfastly set his face to goto\nJerusalem.\u201d\n\"And sent messengers be\nfore his face: and they went,\nand entered into a village of\nthe Samaritans, to make\nready for him.\"\n\"And they did not receive\nhim. because his face was\nas though he would go to\nJerusalem.\u201d\n\"And when his disciples\nJames and John saw this,\nthey said, Lord, wilt thou\nthat we command fire to\ncome down from heaven,\nand consume them, even as\nElias did?\u201d\n\"But he turned, and re\nbuked them, and said, Ye\nknow not what manner of\nspirit ye are of.\u201d\nFor tha Son of man is\nnot coma to dastroy man's\nlivas, but to sava them.\nAnd they went to another\nvillage.\u201d (Luke 9:51-56)\n\nPRESIDENT DWIGHT DAVID EISENHOWER\nTha Whita Housa\nWashington, D.C.\nDaar Mr. Prasidant:\nWa baliava you will find comfort, spiritual strength,\nand support from tha anclosad copy of our latter to Mr.\nSherman Adams.\nA brief excerpt therefrom may be of immediate comfort,\nquoting Aba Lincoln to his admirers, when both condemned\nind praised: 'Gentlemen, I frankly confess, I did not control\njvents, they controlled me'\nTHAT JULY Ist STEEL WORKERS\nRAISE IN PAY\u2014\"S JULY STEEL PRICE\nBOOST IS FORECAST\"\u2014Detroit News\n(clipping anclosad)\nDaar Mr. Prasidant: If that raise is not stopped, as you\nknow, recovery will be seriously interfered with and you\nhave more political power, by tha grace of God, than anyont\nelse on tha horizon. Need wa say more?\nBast wishes.\nInspirationally your#,\naccording to Christ,\nAndrew F. Fruahauf, C.S.\nJune 19, 1958\nHON. SHERMAN ADAMS, ASST. PRESIDENT\nThe Whita Housa\nWashington, D. C.\nDaar Mr. Adams:\nSt. Paul said: 'lf wa give you spiritual things, is it\ngreat thing if you give us your carnal things?'\nYou have bean Mr. Barnard Goldfine's 'guardian angel.*\nHEBREWS HAVE GOT TO HAVE FRIENDS,\nLIKE YOU AND ME, ETC.\nTHEIR SPIRITUAL SANITY DEMANDS IT!\nYou, the Prasidant, and Mr, Goldfina, could declare,\ndid Aba Lincoln, whan both condemned and praised: G* n\ntlaman, I frankly confess, I did not control events, they\ncontrolled me'!\nTha RETURN of Christ and Jesus, 90 years ago!, ,h\n(Sea SHERMAN ADAMS, Page 2)\nLabor News\nEMPLOYER NON-RED OATH 'DISMAYING'\nTO N. L R. B. !C\n(N. Y. Tribune, 6/W\u00bb\nWASHINGTON, June 19 (AP)\u2014Congress was told today\ntha Senate-passed labor bill would at least double the to\n\u2022\u2022ready above $300,000 annually, of administering the\nTaft-Hartley law non-Communist oath requirement.\nThe Senate voted to require employers to file oaths th*\nthey are not Communist party members to qualify r\nrights administered by the National Labor Relations B\u00b0 ar\nAt present, under the Taft-Hartley act, the oath requiremertt\napplies only to union officials. The House has not yet cti\non the bill.\nBoyd Leedom, N. L. R. 8., told a House Labor subcom\nmittee there are many more employers than union off' cl4\nand the board would bo \"dismayed\" If It had to t#od\noath administration to them.\nDETROIT\nCLEAR THINKING\nREQUIRED\nThe thoughts of the disci\nples at that time, were not\nas clear as Jesus would have\nthem to be. So he wanted\nthem not to judge unrighte\nously, or rather, \"judge not 1\nat all. In the meantime, he\nwanted them at all times to\nbe able to separate good\nfrom evil.\nAnd thus thinking on the\ngood side, which at all times\nhelps to supply with quality\nand full quantity, the dis\ntinction, between good and\nbad.\n\nCHOOSE THE GOOD\nJesus knew that choosing\nthe good things of life, mor\nal, immortal ideas, would\nfollow, w hich thoughts would\nhelp to evangelize the world.\nThis inspiration is here with\n(Continued on Page 4)\nJune 19, 1958","height":"27921","width":"18372"}}
